{"tid":893003,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"小狗太瘦，用曬所有方法都谷唔肥","createTime":"2018-11-07T09:39:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T16:02:12.000Z","uid":80424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"edf9298827a7cd9c9bb30db4afa6225369893b1b","tid":893003,"uid":80424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:39:44.000Z","msg":"有2隻柴犬，其中一隻由細到大都唔識肥<br />\n食bb糧、蒸雞肉、蒸羊肉、食魚油、飲羊奶乜都唔得，都係瘦<br />\n(唔打算餵生肉)<br />\n每日落街2次，有曬下太陽，<br />\n間唔時去狗公園放電<br />\n佢身體又冇乜特別差，<br />\n但個個話佢好瘦，幫佢沖涼嗰個又係咁講<br />\n仲有咩方法可以谷肥佢？"},{"pid":"029bdf220f1103516bae9343b6b1f09da3bb5fe7","tid":893003,"uid":46038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"屎如何？"},{"pid":"17105aa02f69dba43d80ef5b517a7b6046399c5d","tid":893003,"uid":80424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"029bdf220f1103516bae9343b6b1f09da3bb5fe7","tid":893003,"uid":46038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:40:46.000Z","msg":"屎如何？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:44:22.000Z","msg":"好正常，深啡色唔太硬唔太軟，一日1至2次"},{"pid":"e04debcb7f893bc32eae2a2b2f6947d170020497","tid":893003,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"帶佢去check下body check"},{"pid":"8cacf3231c03957dc02d0a8358b6aa2f2eba4769","tid":893003,"uid":32279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"個時隻老狗慢慢咁輕<br />\n啲人係咁話因為老唔吸收<br />\n跟著醫生話跌幅唔算好大 唔洗擔心<br />\n隔左一輪就有日唔食野即刻睇急症<br />\n原來胰臟炎 要住院<br />\n胰臟炎好番 即刻重番<br />\n所以身體檢查下好啲"},{"pid":"582fd51e629b808b960587ba28f44180f3e3e904","tid":893003,"uid":212153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:50:45.000Z","msg":"杜左蟲未"},{"pid":"5f022d0e098a8bb37fc6b397ac682982b88a4092","tid":893003,"uid":145829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"有冇相睇呀？"},{"pid":"131624592e8a1aac98b62f48d95b0e300aefeabf","tid":893003,"uid":80424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"